description:
Season Six Match

AMBER RAYNE
Rogue
HT: 5’3
WT: 108lbs
Season record (1-0)
Lifetime record (4-2)
Ranked 10th

YANA JORDAN
The Wildcat
HT: 5’6
WT: 135lbs
Season record (1-1)
Lifetime record (1-1)
Ranked 13th

The Rogue is back after leading her Tag Team to 3rd place in the 2008 season. She is eager to get back into the single match style and looks forward to the tournament, but first she has to get past The Wildcat.

Many think that Yana is underrated. Many think she is better then what we have seen so far. This match will tell us what we need to know about the Wildcat.

With Amber giving up 27lbs to a muscular Wildcat, will her experience be enough to stop an ass fucking in RD4? Amber puts up a good fight, but brutal leg scissors sap the strength from her as Yana takes what she wants from her smaller opponent.
title: Amber "Rogue" Rayne (1-0) vs Yana "The Wildcat" Jordan (1-1)
